<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rules & Guidelines</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style2.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.7/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-LN+7fdVzj6u52u30Kp6M/trliBMCMKTyK833zpbD+pXdCLuTusPj697FH4R/5mcr" crossorigin="anonymous">

</head>
<body>
    <%-include("../includes/header/header")%>
        <div class="container-lg">
            <div class="form-wrapper-md">
                <div class="row mt-3" >
                    <div class="guideline-heading d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
                        <h2 class="heading fw-bold">Community Guidelines</h2>
                        <p class="text-center">Please follow these guidelines to help maintain a positive and helpful community environment.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card col-lg-8 col-md-6 col-sm-10 m-auto mt-4 mb-3" >
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="card-title px-1 pt-1 pb-2">
                                <h3 class="fw-semibold">General Guidelines</h3>
                            </div>
                            <div class="genral-guideline-div card-text lh-lg m-auto mt-0">
                                    <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span> <span class="content ">&nbsp; Be respectful and courteous to all community members</span> <br>
                                    <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span> <span class="content">&nbsp; Use clear, descriptive titles for your posts</span> <br>
                                    <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span> <span class="content">&nbsp; Provide accurate and truthful information</span> <br>
                                    <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span> <span class="content">&nbsp; Keep posts relevant to the community</span> <br>
                                    <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span> <span class="content">&nbsp; No spam, advertising, or promotional content</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card col-lg-8 col-md-6 col-sm-10 m-auto mt-4 mb-3" >
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="card-title px-1 pt-1 pb-2">
                                <h3 class="fw-semibold">Content Standards</h3>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-text lh-lg">
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; No offensive, discriminatory, or inappropriate language</span> <br>
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; No personal attacks or harassment</span> <br>
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; Respect privacy - don't share personal information of others</span> <br>
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; No illegal activities or content</span> <br>
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; Keep discussions constructive and helpful</span>  
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card col-lg-8 col-md-6 col-sm-10 m-auto mt-4 mb-3">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="card-title px-1 pt-1 pb-2">
                                <h3 class="fw-semibold">Lost & Found</h3>
                            </div>
                            <div class=" card-text lh-lg">
                                
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; Include clear descriptions and contact information</span> <br>
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; Remove posts once items are found/returned</span> <br>
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; Be cautious when meeting strangers</span> <br>
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; Verify ownership before returning valuable items</span>

                                
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card col-lg-8 col-md-6 col-sm-10 m-auto mt-4 mb-3">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="card-title px-1 pt-1 pb-2">
                                <h3 class="fw-semibold">Events</h3>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-text lh-lg">
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; Include date, time, and location details</span> <br>
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; Update or remove posts for cancelled events</span> <br>
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; Ensure events comply with community guidelines</span> <br>
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; Provide contact information for questions</span> <br>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card col-lg-8 col-md-6 col-sm-10 m-auto mt-4 mb-3">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="card-title px-1 pt-1 pb-2">
                                <h3 class="fw-semibold">Urgent Notices</h3>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-text lh-lg">
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; Only use for genuine emergencies or urgent matters</span> <br>
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; Provide clear, actionable information</span> <br>
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; Include contact details for immediate response</span> <br>
                                <span class="mark bg-primary d-inline-block rounded-circle"> </span><span class="content">&nbsp; Update posts with new information as needed</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card col-lg-8 col-md-6 col-sm-10 m-auto mt-4 mb-3">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <div class="card-title px-1 pt-1 pb-2 mx-auto">
                                <h3 class="fw-semibold" >Enforcement</h3>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-text lh-lg">
                                <p >Posts that violate these guidelines may be removed without notice. Repeated violations may result in restricted posting privileges.</p>
                                <p>If you see content that violates these guidelines, please use the Contact/Feedback section to report it to the moderators.</p>
                                <p class="text-primary fw-normal">Thank you for helping to keep our community notice board a safe and helpful space for everyone!</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    
</body>
</html>
